"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This is a basic recipe for authentic Italian tomato sauce flavored with extra-virgin olive oil, garlic and basil. Toss with your favorite pasta or use for pizza, gnocchi and more.\\n\\n[ \\n ](https://www.allrecipes.com/cook/SilviaG%C2%BBSilviaG/)\\n\\n2 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil\\n1 onion, chopped\\n4 cloves garlic, halved\\n2 (14 ounce) cans passata (crushed tomatoes)\\nÂ¼ cup fresh basil, torn in half\\nsalt to taste\\n\\n## Directions\\n\\nInstructions Checklist\\n\\n* Step 1\\n\\n  Heat oil in a saucepan over low heat. Add onion and garlic. Cook and stir until soft and translucent, about 5 minutes. Add passata, basil, and salt. Cover and simmer over medium heat, stirring occasionally, until tomato sauce has thickened, about 20 minutes. Remove garlic halves before serving.\",\"timestamp\":1640343988,\"title\":\"Sugo di Pomodoro\"},\"digest\":\"eniiPZQPEznneRYrsDZkh87XcHGSfCTGHcNqVC8i8PY\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x60AD21cAb36bb6DC4Da025BaF7e98a6fA5C47AF6\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dUvSjGhJ_fwnkWI4C-ExWLO91gELWa2xfLWzr79py6s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5CEoEFCGyl0cED3kHZ3zbHq7iGP8fMPcWafIJfUHdag\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"6kbzenpHan2v-_3x7f5geqbYOQQPhz9SeW1trpEhw4naNycck55jDwMPQBXLFK3fYf2GffWJYAX-f9LWTrL2nw\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4fedc1b4ed4f0ec923e1959f45cf83b3b928b28fbc049df525ebb4499dff2c882154b01a7f24fcb3040124f99ca988201595bafb1e18d506387dff4a6d0c04b01b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"dUvSjGhJ_fwnkWI4C-ExWLO91gELWa2xfLWzr79py6s\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"5CEoEFCGyl0cED3kHZ3zbHq7iGP8fMPcWafIJfUHdag\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"eniiPZQPEznneRYrsDZkh87XcHGSfCTGHcNqVC8i